New Records: Jean-Philippe Krasso scored his third goal in these Afcon qualifiers
Key Match Events: Jean-Philippe Krasso scored a goal in injury time before the interval
Oumar Diakite doubled Ivory Coast's lead 10 minutes into the second half
Post-Match Reflections: Ivory Coast made it two wins from as many 2025 Africa Cup of Nations (Afcon) qualifying matches
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Elephants top Group G with a full haul of six points
Others: Ivory Coast defeated Chad 2-0 at the Ahmadou Ahidjo Stadium in Yaounde, Cameroon, on Tuesday night
